   "html": "\n[ どいはら・けんじ ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n教育総監、航空総監、奉天特務機関長、奉天市長、陸軍大将、Ａ級戦犯"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"04t.html\">一覧　（タ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　岡山県出身。陸士卒。陸大卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　天津特務機関勤務などを経て、満州事変直後、奉天市長に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　天津で中国人による反<a href=\"../p/cyogakur.html\">張学良</a>暴動を起こさせ、<a href=\"../p/fugi.html\">溥儀</a>を満州に移送。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　奉天特務機関長として内蒙工作を進め、<a href=\"../1935/06doiha.html\">土肥原・秦徳純協定を締結</a>。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　第12方面軍司令官として<a href=\"../1945/08gyoku.html\">終戦</a>を迎える。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、Ａ級戦犯として<a href=\"../1948/11tokyo.html\">東京裁判で「絞首刑」の判決</a>。<a href=\"../1948/12senpa.html\">刑死</a>。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
